title: Ep - 124 - DANNY PELLEGRINO REVIEWS 90 DAY FIANCÉ: BEFORE THE 90 DAYS
description:
Danny Pellegrino from Everything Iconic podcast helps Kate review the prequel to TLC’s “90 Day Fiancé.” The show features couples in an international relationship and how they first became acquainted. From the initial in-person meeting to traveling to a faraway country, the stories of these potential spouses-to-be uncover sometimes insurmountable hurdles.


Reality Life with Kate Casey
